en_151105_0	A man has died after being hit by a van that was stolen at a liquor store in Badulla last night.
en_151105_1	The deceased was a father of four from Badulupitiya area in Badulla.
en_151105_2	Police has arrested the 27-year-old man who was stealing the van.
en_151105_3	The van owner has visited a house after leaving the vehicle with its key on it.
en_151105_4	Police investigations are underway to arrest another person who was in the van during the incident.
